<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <meta charset="utf-8">
    <title>Your MyTrackr Verification Code</title>
    <style>
        body { font-family: 'Inter', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; background-color: #f4f4f5; margin: 0; padding: 0; }
        .container { max-width: 600px; margin: 40px auto; background-color: #ffffff; border-radius: 8px; overflow: hidden; box-shadow: 0 4px 6px rgba(0,0,0,0.05); }
        .header { background-color: #101828; color: #ffffff; padding: 20px 40px; text-align: center; }
        .logo { font-size: 24px; font-weight: bold; margin: 0; }
        .content { padding: 40px; color: #344054; line-height: 1.6; text-align: center; }
        .otp-box { background-color: #f2f4f7; border: 1px solid #d0d5dd; border-radius: 8px; padding: 20px; font-size: 32px; font-weight: bold; letter-spacing: 4px; color: #101828; display: inline-block; margin: 20px 0; }
        .footer { background-color: #f9fafb; padding: 20px 40px; text-align: center; color: #667085; font-size: 14px; border-top: 1px solid #eaecf0; }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="header">
            <h2 class="logo">MyTrackr</h2>
        </div>
        <div class="content">
            <h1 style="color: #101828; margin-top: 0;">Verification Code</h1>
            <p>Hello {{name}},</p>
            <p>Use the following 6-digit code to verify your account and complete your registration. This code will expire in 15 minutes.</p>
            <div class="otp-box">
                {{otp}}
            </div>
            <p>If you didn't request this code, you can safely ignore this email.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="footer">
            <p>&copy; 2026 MyTrackr. All rights reserved.</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
